Acceptance Corp.: 7.775% 30 to 44 days; 7.725% 45 to 59 days;
7.675% 60 to 89 days; 7.625% 90 to 119 days; 7.60% 120 to 149
days; 7.55% 150 to 179 days; 7.50% 180 to 209 days; 7.45% 210
to 270 days.
                                                                                                       

   COMMERCIAL PAPER: High-grade unsecured notes sold through
dealers by major corporations in multiples of $1,000: 7.88%
30 days; 7.83% 60 days; 7.75% 90 days.
                                                                                                       

   CERTIFICATES OF DEPOSIT: 7.67% one month; 7.69% two
