28.5%. Energy Service said the two groups expect to complete
that purchase by Oct. 31.
   Energy Service said the two rigs are currently operating
in the Gulf of Mexico, and are expected to be moved to the
North Sea by Wilrig. As part of the pact, Wilrig has options
to purchase three additional rigs.
